### 2-3. Repository 코드

**파일 위치: `domain/src/main/kotlin/com/maum/backend/repository/user/`**

```kotlin
// UserRepository.kt
interface UserRepository : JpaRepository<UserEntity, String> {
    fun findByPhoneNumber(phoneNumber: String): UserEntity?
    fun findByIdAndStatus(id: String, status: Int): UserEntity?
}

// UserProfileRepository.kt
interface UserProfileRepository : JpaRepository<UserProfileEntity, String> {
    fun findByUserId(userId: String): UserProfileEntity?
}

// UserPhotoRepository.kt
interface UserPhotoRepository : JpaRepository<UserPhotoEntity, String> {
    fun findByUserIdAndStatusOrderByOrder(userId: String, status: Int): List<UserPhotoEntity>
}
```

**파일 위치: `domain/src/main/kotlin/com/maum/backend/repository/call/`**

```kotlin
// VoiceCallRepository.kt
interface VoiceCallRepository : JpaRepository<VoiceCallEntity, String> {
    fun findByCallerIdOrReceiverIdOrderByCreatedAtDesc(
        callerId: String,
        receiverId: String
    ): List<VoiceCallEntity>
    fun findByIdAndStatus(id: String, status: Int): VoiceCallEntity?
}
```

**파일 위치: `domain/src/main/kotlin/com/maum/backend/repository/match/`**

```kotlin
// MatchRequestRepository.kt
interface MatchRequestRepository : JpaRepository<MatchRequestEntity, String> {
    fun findByReceiverIdAndStatus(receiverId: String, status: Int): List<MatchRequestEntity>
    fun findBySenderIdAndReceiverIdAndStatus(
        senderId: String,
        receiverId: String,
        status: Int
    ): MatchRequestEntity?
}
```

